%%{ init: { "sequence": { "mirrorActors": false } } }%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant HF as HuggingFace / GitHub
    participant ING as Ingestion Service
    participant LLM as LLM
    participant EMB as Embedding Service
    participant MC as Model Cards / Data Sheet Service

    HF->>ING: Webhook (new model / update)
    ING->>HF: Fetch README + metadata
    HF-->>ING: Raw content
    ING->>LLM: Extract structured fields
    LLM-->>ING: Structured model card draft
    ING->>EMB: Check for duplicates
    EMB-->>ING: Similar existing cards
    alt Duplicate found
        ING->>MC: Update existing card
    else New card
        ING->>MC: Create model card / data sheet
    end
